// define UDF functions
def toYear(s : String): Int = if (s.isEmpty) 0 else (s.slice(0, 0 + 4)).toInt
def toMonth(s : String): Int = if (s.isEmpty) 0 else (s.slice(4, 4 + 2)).toInt
def toDay(s : String): Int = if (s.isEmpty) 0 else (s.slice(6, 6 + 2)).toInt

def getTone(tones: String): Double = tones.split(",")(0).toDouble

// define UDF
val udfToYear = udf(toYear _)
val udfToMonth = udf(toMonth _)
val udfToDay = udf(toDay _)

val udfGetTone = udf(getTone _)

// Load events
val rddEventsEng = sc.binaryFiles("s3://aouani-habib-telecom-gdelt2019/201912[0-9]*.export.CSV.zip"). // charger quelques fichers via une regex
   flatMap {  // decompresser les fichiers
       case (name: String, content: PortableDataStream) =>
          val zis = new ZipInputStream(content.open)
          Stream.continually(zis.getNextEntry).
                takeWhile{case null => zis.close(); false 
                            case _ => true}.
                flatMap { _ =>
                    val br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(zis))
                    Stream.continually(br.readLine()).takeWhile(_ != null)
                }
    }

val dfEventsEng = rddEventsEng.map(x => x.split("\t")).map(row => row.mkString(";")).map(x => x.split(";")).toDF()

// Load events (Translated)
val rddEventsTrans = sc.binaryFiles("s3://aouani-habib-telecom-gdelt2019/201912[0-9]*.translation.export.CSV.zip"). // charger quelques fichers via une regex
   flatMap {  // decompresser les fichiers
       case (name: String, content: PortableDataStream) =>
          val zis = new ZipInputStream(content.open)
          Stream.continually(zis.getNextEntry).
                takeWhile{case null => zis.close(); false 
                            case _ => true}.
                flatMap { _ =>
                    val br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(zis))
                    Stream.continually(br.readLine()).takeWhile(_ != null)
                }
    }

val dfEventsTrans = rddEventsTrans.map(x => x.split("\t")).map(row => row.mkString(";")).map(x => x.split(";")).toDF()

// make union
val dfEvents = dfEventsEng.union(dfEventsTrans)

// Select columns and cast
val dfEventsSelect = dfEvents
    .withColumn("_tmp", $"value")
    .select($"_tmp".getItem(0).as("eventid"),
            udfToYear($"_tmp".getItem(1)).as("year"),
            udfToMonth($"_tmp".getItem(1)).as("month"),
            udfToDay($"_tmp".getItem(1)).as("day"),
            $"_tmp".getItem(7).as("actor1countrycode"),
            $"_tmp".getItem(17).as("actor2countrycode"),
            $"_tmp".getItem(34).as("avgtone"),
            $"_tmp".getItem(40).as("actor1geolat"),
            $"_tmp".getItem(41).as("actor1geolong"),
            $"_tmp".getItem(48).as("actor2geolat"),
            $"_tmp".getItem(49).as("actor2geolong"))
    .withColumn("eventid", $"eventid".cast("Int"))        
    .withColumn("avgtone", $"avgtone".cast("Float"))
    .withColumn("actor1geolat", $"actor1geolat".cast("Float"))
    .withColumn("actor1geolong", $"actor1geolong".cast("Float"))
    .withColumn("actor2geolat", $"actor2Geolat".cast("Float"))
    .withColumn("actor2geolong", $"actor2geolong".cast("Float"))
    .filter($"actor1countrycode" !== "")
    .filter($"actor2countrycode" !== "")
    

dfEventsSelect.printSchema()
